{"tid":1297680,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[回到雪地與花開之時]十七日日本首次獨遊","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:11:04.000Z","uid":135113,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"949764f232fefe408940256e76ed515be2309e7c","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"個標題引咗你入嚟唔好意思，但最近發夢發到好無力，開下手機Album睇相就突然想出個遊記當畀自己分散下注意力，咁先可以繼續發夢支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁話說本人舊年開始唔開心，搞搞下就連學都休埋，屋企人見我無嘢做就建議我去轉旅行，而我又未睇過雪同櫻花，所以就揀咗三月去<br />\n<br />\n行程有十七日我懶得逐日打出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去咗北海道同東京，超鍾意北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（後話：所以五月又去咗轉北海道）<br />\n<br />\n同埋本人唔想坐jr超過三個鐘，所以內陸機係我好朋友<br />\n<br />\n放少少圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSrfwHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSrfwHb.png&h=04634bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvjpp2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhvjpp2d.png&h=13de9b97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MVHbHe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MVHbHe.png&h=6a69bb01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4add2OV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4add2OV.png&h=7c01a2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGVoFAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnGVoFAC.png&h=42aec923&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BaaLTVE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBaaLTVE.png&h=e4fef549&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31afb56bacff184ef44dcd58f82a2595e5dd1087","tid":1297680,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"795336a0e6a4c00dc5a9200732d22464c91e5555","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:21:55.000Z","msg":"Day1 14March<br />\n<br />\nHKG-NRT-CTS<br />\n<br />\n點解唔直航？<br />\n因為cx好貴，又怕hx執，結果坐咗兩程JL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋就係轉機先有得睇下飛機同黃昏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQZwPGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQZwPGX.png&h=a78727f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於落機後又有雪又有喼要推，又唔知而家嘅自己會出個遊記<br />\n<br />\n所以無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話明獨遊，但間酒店畀間twin bed我，真係獨對空床，影都費事影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔多覺香港有呢隻味就買嚟飲下，試過就算<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOFjYG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOFjYG4.png&h=29f05b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e07157e15745657bf775d2fb33492165a707bed","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"Day2 15March<br />\n<br />\n余市小樽<br />\n<br />\n一早起身就行去時計台對面巴士站等車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人同我一樣覺得香港鐘樓靚過時計台好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNk0Jbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNk0Jbs.png&h=9c5ae4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐完兩個幾鐘巴士就到余市，趁同場嘅港女仲叫緊男友影橡木桶，影到張無人嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrby3bu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjrby3bu.png&h=f886b1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒鬼如我，就梗係飲下先再落樓買<br />\n隔幾枱有兩對香港中年夫婦無啦啦話乜有女仔會一個去旅行嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要笑到勁大聲以為我唔識聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tUk4qwc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtUk4qwc.png&h=dd1b1380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買完酒就坐返函館本線出小樽，已經係喺北海道期間坐得最耐jr嘅一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2CZer3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2CZer3.png&h=28260c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊手宮線遺址<br />\n由張圖可以睇出天氣幾差，事實上之後都突然間落咗勁大雪，保護相機重要過自己嘅我於是又無影低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbvoFYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbvoFYg.png&h=1cb625cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行完幾間特產鋪就行去排LeTao食個tea<br />\n我：寫個靚名排隊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解成張紙得我一個係一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9PMDKY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9PMDKY.png&h=82b52579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但一個人旅行嘅好處就係想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食得慢，好好享受先係重點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVfoFYk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVfoFYk.png&h=4b5a0f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就等天黑影運河，食風食到飽就返札幌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgfzNDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgfzNDp.png&h=383114d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7869a04bdfcb48b54dd0361874b1c954586ab59a","tid":1297680,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名<br />\n睇開啲放鬆下或者plan下下一個旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b936fff2ee384e6437bee265c87ba593b64b93d0","tid":1297680,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"行程?"},{"pid":"0ad1029ddd2e6f071609943164c5367a69409eeb","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b936fff2ee384e6437bee265c87ba593b64b93d0","tid":1297680,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"行程?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"八日喺北海道嘅札幌稚內函館<br />\n九日喺東京同埋近郊地區行下<br />\n<br />\nSor無寫開遊記開頭無打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b716d6b53ae858ed4768d383e5607649f0d47a9f","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7869a04bdfcb48b54dd0361874b1c954586ab59a","tid":1297680,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名<br />\n睇開啲放鬆下或者plan下下一個旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:03:39.000Z","msg":"今年去咗兩次北海道都仲係想去<br />\n可能下個旅行都係北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6890b8d1b56053192a3014df65a2ff27fd28c3c1","tid":1297680,"uid":135113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T20:04:22.000Z","msg":"Day3 16March<br />\n<br />\n話說我喺香港朝早六點先瞓，去到日本係六點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就晨運咁經大通行去圓山公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0zWem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0zWem.png&h=35705bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實就去下北海道神宮參拜，但佢個雪景真係點影都靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zvn6Nk3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvn6Nk3.png&h=93b54c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後由圓山公園行去札幌站啲商場行下，就坐個站去札幌啤酒博物館<br />\nBtw個館好多展版都係得日文，全程看圖說故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0DebNK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0DebNK.png&h=55c0b554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一場嚟到點都飲返杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxGGBer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxGGBer.png&h=821ce9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHea陣就返狸小路食湯咖哩，飲落油到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44mGBet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44mGBet.png&h=b0b61d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食滯咗就行去影電視塔，點知一出地下街一分鐘就突然大雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我第日走㗎喇，點解連個天都唔畀我影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等咗陣都無停雪跡象，認命返酒店執行李<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmhKy09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmhKy09.png&h=39fc7647&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2fe7e6d5492bceb8a22409fa53ee3295956506b","tid":1297680,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"1f2b36f4c071893072584e1280ee21f457a272db","tid":1297680,"uid":7070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"幫推，想睇東京個幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea8544f7f2ae36d461a4477a5d932133d029d9b","tid":1297680,"uid":31634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意北海道，我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"84bc7fd043d353dfbf5aaa21d44831095adc0d82","tid":1297680,"uid":38195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"落雪的札幌真係靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2316e151e56046ac451c48c61df8cdbe48ab3a0d","tid":1297680,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"樓主人呢"}]}